articles.title: Gift to Kim Jong Il from President of Asian Olympic Council
articles.content:
Gift to Kim Jong Il from President of Asian Olympic Council

					Pyongyang, November 21 (KCNA) -- Leader Kim Jong Il received a gift from the president of the Asian Olympic Council on a visit to the DPRK.
					
					The gift was handed to Kim Yong Nam, president of the Presidium of the Supreme People's Assembly, by Sheikh Ahmad Al Fahad Al Sabah, president of the Asian Olympic Council, on Monday.

articles.title: Gift to Kim Jong Il from Kuwaiti Emir
articles.content:
Gift to Kim Jong Il from Kuwaiti Emir

					Pyongyang, November 21 (KCNA) -- Leader Kim Jong Il was presented with a gift by Sheikh Sabah Al－Ahmad Al－Jaber Al－Sabah, emir of Kuwait. 
					
					The gift was handed over to Kim Yong Nam, president of the Presidium of the Supreme People's Assembly, by Sheikh Ahmad Al Fahad Al Sabah, president of the Asian Olympic Council who is on a visit to the DPRK, on Monday.
